#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:117
msgid "Firmware Update"
msgstr ""
"固件更新"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:119
msgid "The installation of the downloaded firmware is initiated using the REST API by issuing a POST request to /mgmt/requests. The information which should be provided is:"
msgstr ""
"需要使用 REST API 向 /mgmt/requests 发出 POST 请求来安装已下载的固件。应提供的信息如下："

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:121
msgid "The action ``firmware/update``"
msgstr ""
"操作“固件/更新”"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:122
msgid "The list of devices to receive the image, all of the same device type"
msgstr ""
"用于接收映像的设备列表（所有设备都属于同一设备类型）"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:124
msgid "The device management server in the Internet of Things Foundation uses the device management protocol to request that the devices specified initiate the firmware installation by publishing using the topic ``iotdm-1/mgmt/initiate/firmware/update``."
msgstr ""
"Internet of Things Foundation 中的设备管理服务器使用设备管理协议，通过使用主题“iotdm-1/mgmt/initiate/firmware/update”发布请求，以请求让所指定设备启动固件安装。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:126
msgid "If this operation can be initiated immediately, ``rc`` should be set to ``202``."
msgstr ""
"如果此操作可以立即启动，那么“rc”应设置为“202”。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:127
msgid "If firmware was not previously downloaded successfully, ``rc`` should be set to ``400``."
msgstr ""
"如果之前未成功下载固件，那么“rc”应设置为“400”。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:128
msgid "If firmware update attempt fails, ``rc`` should be set to ``500`` and the ``message`` field can optionally be set to contain relevant information."
msgstr ""
"如果固件更新尝试失败，那么“rc”应设置为“500”，并可以选择设置“message”字段来包含相关信息。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:129
msgid "If firmware update is not supported ``rc`` should be set to ``501`` and the ``message`` field can optionally be set to contain relevant information."
msgstr ""
"如果固件更新不受支持，那么“rc”应设置为“501”，并可以选择设置“message”字段来包含相关信息。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:130
msgid "If ``mgmt.firmware.state`` is not ``2`` (Downloaded), an error should be reported with ``rc`` set to ``400`` and an optional message text."
msgstr ""
"如果“mgmt.firmware.state”不为“2”（已下载），那么将报告一个错误，其中将“rc”设置为“400”并返回可选消息文本。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:131
msgid "Otherwise, ``mgmt.firmware.updateStatus`` should be set to ``1`` (In Progress) and firmware installation should start."
msgstr ""
"否则，“mgmt.firmware.updateStatus”应设置为“1”（进行中）并将启动固件安装。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:132
msgid "If firmware installation fails, ``mgmt.firmware.updateStatus`` should be set to either:"
msgstr ""
"如果固件安装失败，那么“mgmt.firmware.updateStatus”应设置为以下任一值："

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:134
msgid "``2`` (Out of Memory)"
msgstr ""
"“2”（内存不足）"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:135
msgid "``5`` (Unsupported Image)"
msgstr ""
"“5”（映像不受支持）"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:137
msgid "Once firmware update is complete, ``mgmt.firmware.updateStatus`` should be set to ``0`` (Success), ``mgmt.firmware.state`` should be set to ``0`` (Idle), downloaded firmware image can be deleted from the device and ``deviceInfo.fwVersion`` should be set to the value of ``mgmt.firmware.version``."
msgstr ""
"完成硬件更新后，“mgmt.firmware.updateStatus”应设置为“0”（成功），“mgmt.firmware.state”应设置为“0”（空闲），可以从设备中删除已下载的固件映像，且“deviceInfo.fwVersion”应设置为“mgmt.firmware.version”的值。"

#: ..\docs\device_mgmt\operations\firmware_actions.rst:139
msgid "All fields under ``mgmt.firmware`` must be set at the same time, so that if there is a current observation for ``mgmt.firmware``, only a single notify message is sent."
msgstr ""
"“mgmt.firmware”下的所有字段必须同时进行设置，如果当前正在观察“mgmt.firmware”，那么只会发送一条通知消息。"

